r test this model by searching for resolved\nsignatures of the warm and slow wide-angle molecular wind that would be\npredicted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2015 16:22:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-23"}
